In parallel, other works studied biases and limitations of the LM-as-KB paradigm (e.g., [cao2021knowledgeable,DBLP:journals/tacl/ElazarKRRHSG21,razniewski2021language,jiang2020can]). In this work, we investigate the feasibility of leveraging LMs to complete real-world KBs, and mainly focus on long-tail facts.